succesfull endpoints



POST - /api/auth/login                   - trainer/admin/user
POST - /api/auth/create-admin


POST - /api/user/register                - User Registration  - Exception - User exists already
GET  - /api/user/{user_id}/performance   - User view his performance
GET  - /api/user/{user_id}/task          - User can view his tasks assigned by trainer
GET  - /api/user/batch/{batch_id}        - User is fetching the batch details by giving the batch_id
POST - /api/user/feedback                - User is giving the feedback about the trainer



POST    - /api/admin/trainers                     - admin register the trainers
GET     - /api/admin/trainers                     - admin view the trainers
DELETE  - /api/admin/trainers/email/{email}       - admin deleting the trainer by giving trainer email
POST    - /api/admin/batches                      - admin creates the batches
GET     - /api/admin/batches                      - admin views the batches
DELETE  - /api/admin/batch/batch_code/{batchCode} - admin deletes the batches 
POST    - /api/admin/stipend                      - admin initiating the stipend to interns 
DELETE  - /api/admin/user/email/{email}           - admin deleting the user by giving users email



GET    - /api/trainer/batches/{trainer_id}    - trainer Fetch the batches by using trainer_id
POST   - /api/trainer/tasks                   - trainer creates a task for the intern
PUT    - /api/trainer/tasks/{task_id}         - trainer is updating the task of the intern from pending to ongoing and from ongoing to completed
DELETE - /api/trainer/tasks/{task_id}         - deleting the task_id
POST   - /api/trainer/attendance              - marking the attendance for the intern
POST   - /api/trainer/performance             - giving the performance details for the particular users
GET    - /api/trainer/UserBatch/{trainer_id}  - trainer can fetch his batch and the corresponding users who registered for that batch

